    <section id="overview">
      <h2>HeyGen Overview &amp; Pricing</h2>
      <p>HeyGen operates on a credit-based SaaS model with five tiers. All pricing below was verified from the official heygen.com/pricing page captured on July 4, 2026. Monthly pricing is shown; annual billing is available at a discount.</p>

      <div class="callout warn">
        <strong>Pricing note:</strong> Pricing was verified from the official website on July 4, 2026. SaaS pricing can change — verify current rates before subscribing. All prices are in USD. Annual billing offers a lower effective monthly rate.
      </div>

      <h3>Pricing Tiers (Monthly Billing)</h3>
      <div class="table-scroll">
