      <h3>Core Workflow: How HeyGen Works</h3>
      <p>The platform follows a straightforward workflow: choose an avatar (or upload a photo to create one), write or paste a script, select a voice and language, customize the visual style (background, music, overlays, branding), and generate the video. The AI Studio text-based editor allows further refinement of tone, delivery, gestures, and emotion before final export.</p>

