      <h3>Key Features</h3>

      <h4>Video Agent</h4>
      <p>Prompt-based video generation: type an idea or description, and the AI generates a complete video with avatar, voiceover, visuals, and music. Consumes 20 credits per minute. The most accessible entry point for new users.</p>

      <h4>AI Studio (Text-Based Editor)</h4>
      <p>The core editing interface. Users control every aspect of the video: avatar selection, script editing, voice and language selection, visual style, gestures, emotion, background music, and captions. Edits are text-based — change the script and the video updates automatically, similar to editing a document.</p>

      <h4>AI Avatars (Photo Avatar, Public Avatar, Digital Twin)</h4>
      <p>Photo Avatar: animate a single still photo into a talking video. Public Avatar: 700+ stock avatars representing diverse demographics. Digital Twin: a personalized avatar cloned from a short self-recorded video — requires filming yourself once, after which the AI generates videos in your likeness without further recording.</p>

      <h4>Video Translation &amp; Dubbing</h4>
      <p>Upload a video and HeyGen translates it into 175+ languages with voice cloning and lip-sync. Audio Dubbing (2 credits/min) translates audio only. Full Video Translation (5 credits/min) adds neural lip-sync so the avatar's mouth movements match the new language. A Brand Glossary maintains consistent terminology across translations.</p>

      <h4>Product Placement &amp; UGC Ads</h4>
